":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T16:32:56.000Z","msg":"2010年3.8提埋倉渣到家下"},{"pid":"0e974b04c8eea603ef0f8411e11411418a330638","tid":436162,"uid":154535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T16:52:11.000Z","msg":"旺角場想賣中環價"},{"pid":"5cba536321f2eb6bbead682c2132e6ed0ed9d362","tid":436162,"uid":51997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T02:38:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"530eee3855b59061f599c663e441374603dd9a8b","tid":436162,"uid":66157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T02:51:07.000Z","msg":"玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【未達底價】朗豪坊辦公大樓流標<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】早前推出招標的旺角地標建築物，朗豪坊辦公大樓流標。<br />\n<br />\n項目7月時，以全球招標形式出售，意向價245億元，每平方呎樓面地價逾35000元，負責標售的物業顧問早前指，有兩至三間中資財團洽購。<br />\n<br />\n最新消息指，入標財團出價均未達底價。<br />\n<br />\n朗豪坊辦公大樓屬鷹君持有逾65%權益的冠君產業信託旗下，對於流標後的安排，集團暫時未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n項目樓高59層，樓面面積77萬平方呎，其中四層樓面於2005年已售出。今次標售的，集中是冠君產業信託旗下55層寫字樓，涉及約70萬平方呎樓面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=241337\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D241337&d=lIJcOy1SdpiccVNprGOqLTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=a0b1602a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D241337&h=6b552d4f\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=241337</a>"},{"pid":"2ed5423dd50e6685641607bd5690c07c49a3652e","tid":436162,"uid":51997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T03:20:30.000Z","msg":"Oops"},{"pid":"25d663846f96cf0109c341b15bea77b5011f109c","tid":436162,"uid":51997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T07:19:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【未達底價】朗豪坊辦公大樓流標<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】早前推出招標的旺角地標建築物，朗豪坊辦公大樓流標。<br />\n<br />\n項目7月時，以全球招標形式出售，意向價245億元，每平方呎樓面地價逾35000元，負責標售的物業顧問早前指，有兩至三間中資財團洽購。<br />\n<br />\n最新消息指，入標財團出價均未達底價。<br />\n<br />\n朗豪坊辦公大樓屬鷹君持有逾65%權益的冠君產業信託旗下，對於流標後的安排，集團暫時未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n項目樓高59層，樓面面積77萬平方呎，其中四層樓面於2005年已售出。今次標售的，集中是冠君產業信託旗下55層寫字樓，涉及約70萬平方呎樓面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=241337\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D241337&d=lIJcOy1SdpiccVNprGOqLTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=a0b1602a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D241337&h=6b552d4f\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=241337</a></blockquote><br />\n出咗通告澄清"}]}